## Remarks  

> [!NOTE]
>  [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/includes/deprecatedcontent-md.md)]  

 <span data-ttu-id="dec47-103">A <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity> zarządza wykonywania działań podrzędnych za pomocą <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext> klas, metod i zdarzeń zdefiniowanych na <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> klasy.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dec47-103">A <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity> manages the execution of its child activities using <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext> class methods and events defined on the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> class.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="dec47-104">Na przykład działanie podrzędne jest zaplanowane na wykonanie <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext.ExecuteActivity%2A> z <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dec47-104">For example, a child activity is scheduled for execution using the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext.ExecuteActivity%2A> of <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dec47-105">A <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity> działania może otrzymać powiadomienie, gdy działanie podrzędne zakończeniu jego wykonywania Subskrybuj <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Closed> zdarzeń zdefiniowane na <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dec47-105">A <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity> activity can be notified when a child activity completes its execution by subscribing to the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Closed> event defined on <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="dec47-106">Środowiska uruchomieniowego przepływu pracy wymusza pewne ograniczenia na <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity> wykonywania najbardziej podstawowe których jest to, że <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity> działania nie można przenieść do <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Closed> stan, jeśli wszystkie działania podrzędne są nadal w <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Executing>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Canceling>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Compensating>, lub <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Faulting>, stan.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dec47-106">The workflow runtime enforces certain constraints on <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity> execution, the most fundamental of which is that a <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity> activity cannot move to the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Closed> state if any child activities are still in a <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Executing>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Canceling>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Compensating>, or <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Faulting>, state.</span></span>  



## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="dec47-107">Ten przykład przedstawia podstawowy `CompositeActivity` , który jest wykonywany jego pierwsze działanie podrzędne do wykonania.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dec47-107">This example shows a basic `CompositeActivity` that executes its first child activity for execution.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dec47-108">Gdy działanie podrzędne przejdzie do stanu zamknięte, działania złożonego jest powiadamiany, a następnie uzupełnia jego wykonywania.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dec47-108">When the child activity moves to the Closed state, the composite activity is notified and then completes its execution.</span></span>  

```csharp  
public class HasOneChildActivity : CompositeActivity  
{  
    protected override ActivityExecutionStatus Execute(ActivityExecutionContext executionContext)  
    {  
        Activity child = this.EnabledActivities[0];  
        child.Closed += this.ChildClosed;  
        executionContext.ExecuteActivity(child);  

        return ActivityExecutionStatus.Executing;  
    }  

    void ChildClosed(object sender, ActivityExecutionStatusChangedEventArgs e)  
    {  
        e.Activity.Closed -= this.ChildClosed;  
        ActivityExecutionContext executionContext = sender as ActivityExecutionContext;  

        executionContext.CloseActivity();  
    }  
}  
```
